ly focused on productivity and performance, the exhibition \u201cMens Sana Negotia Prospera\u201d celebrates the interconnection between mental well-being and business success through contemporary art, highlighting how creativity and art can become powerful catalysts for personal and professional growth.\n\nMental well-being and professional success are not separate entities, but rather influence each other, and art can act as a bridge between them.\n\nThe works presented in this exhibition, explore a wide range of themes and concepts legal to mental health and corporate culture. Through paintings, sculptures and installations, the artists offer a broad perspective on how mental well-being can influence productivity, creativity and innovation in the workplace.", "short_description": "In a world increasingly focused on productivity and performance, the exhibition \u201cMens Sana Negotia Prospera\u201d celebrates the interconnection between mental well-being and business success through contemporary art, highlighting how creativity and art can become powerful catalysts for personal and professional growth."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Landscape Square.png", "id": "7676705429016793", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974758_7676705435683459_5694227846487674429_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=s5bda0T5ogoQ7kNvgE44Elj&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDIqlfOKSWSWO2ig3hr5w0GVCmiW80Odj8QMVbVxh42pA&oe=67750D7F"}, {"file_name": "Landscape Mini.png", "id": "1651716732320041", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035324_1651716735653374_7302655488323977148_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=w-VL08UTpJUQ7kNvgG57iWy&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAiDsytff5VvQzDdteQl7MqzdxgJ2lZHSOBxvv6wrgqww&oe=67751E1A"}, {"file_name": "Landscape.png", "id": "1176609033786432", "imag