com&oh=00_AYCXsFmwSvindgpNghJ-ANLVpyKOzPfEO5mbCDrZXhytog&oe=67751A56"}, "display_name": "Mens Sana Negotia Prospera", "keywords": ["MensSana", "JustWare", "Stelva", "Art", "Museum"], "long_description": "In a world increasingly focused on productivity and performance, the exhibition \u2018Mens Sana Negotia Prospera\u2019 celebrates the interconnection between mental well-being and business success through contemporary art, highlighting how creativity and art can become powerful catalysts for personal and professional growth.\n\nMental wellbeing and professional success are not separate entities, but rather they influence each other and art can act as a bridge between them.\n\nThe works presented in this exhibition explore a wide range of themes and concepts related to mental health and corporate culture. Through paintings, sculptures and installations, the artists offer a broad perspective on how mental well-being can influence productivity, creativity and innovation in the workplace.", "short_description": "In a world increasingly focused on productivity and performance, the exhibition \u2018Mens Sana Negotia Prospera\u2019 celebrates the interconnection between mental well-being and business success through contemporary art, highlighting how creativity and art can become powerful catalysts for personal and professional growth."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Landscape Mini.png", "id": "1560560527835448", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75210897_1560560531168781_1895289378269935781_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=k2e-rIFjjZ8Q7kNvgEjjMxw&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAApFhTRLF1tq2q83ZzlLXwQtLU8zQP9zQ1F8ce2k5TSw&oe=67750D5E"}, {"file_name": "Logo.png", "id": "1418845709511738", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974645_1418845712845071_8240363822217321630_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_n